data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this charming two-story brick house offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. How about this brand-new Metal standing seam roof that comes with a lifetime transferable warranty? As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room adorned with a classic brick fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for gatherings with guests. The well-appointed kitchen boasts ample cabinet space and a convenient breakfast nook, making meal preparation a breeze. You'll find three generously sized bedrooms, each offering plenty of space for relaxation and personalization. The primary suite is located on the first floor and features its own private bath, providing a serene retreat after a long day. Outside, the screened-in porch is the perfect spot for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding in the evening while overlooking the lush backyard. With plenty of grassy space and a shed for storage, this backyard is ideal for outdoor activities and gardening enthusiasts alike. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping, this home offers the perfect combination of convenience and comfort. Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful property your own! Schedule a showing today and start envisioning your future in this beautiful brick abode.
